metadata.title: RA Family: Is it possible to incorporate the CK-RA6M5 or CK-RX65N into products?

sections.content:
Question:
Is it possible to incorporate the CK-RA6M5 or CK-RX65N into products?
Answer:
No, the Renesas RX65N Cloud Kit is intended for development and evaluation. It is not intended to be incorporated into products.
Suitable Products
RA6M5,
RX65N/RX651
